    "Email: Resend ($20/mo for 50k emails)",
    "Payment: Stripe Checkout (built-in Alipay/WeChat) — Phase 2",
    "Script sandbox: RestrictedPython + module whitelist + 10s timeout",
    "Signal generation: Single source of truth function shared by SignalEngine and BacktestService"
